data.description:
CHARMING & FURNISHED Home in the Highly Desired Ski Hi Community! This 2 Bed / 2 Bath cabin is absolutely adorable with a true country/farm house style. The Great Room with vaulted ceilings opens into the Dining and Kitchen with laminate flooring throughout. The Kitchen has tons of storage and counter space! The large, Master bedroom has an ensuite bathroom and tons of natural lighting! The second bedroom is also oversized, giving you ample space! Enjoy the cool mountain air on the fabulous covered deck with panoramic views! There are 2 covered decks, front and back. Wonderful privacy. Beautifully landscaped with amazing curb appeal. Metal roof & easy care smart siding! This home is move in ready. You don't want to miss this adorable well constructed 2020 home! Click ''more''... Sky Hi Retreat community is surrounded by National Forest with an abundance of hiking, biking and ATV trails.

Across the street is the National Forest and behind the home is open views.

TRUE PRIDE OF OWNERSHIP!

Imagine living in the White Mountains of Arizona where you have 4 beautiful seasons and where you can breathe in the fresh mountain air and enjoy the 40 lakes and over 600 miles of rivers and streams. In addition to the amazing fishing, this area has one of the most extensive trail systems in the south west for hiking, biking, horseback riding, quading and more. Sunrise Ski Resort is also just 40 minutes away with 3 beautiful mountains to ski, snow board or sled. If shopping is your interest, you will love the antique stores and the multitude of arts and craft shows that happen in the summer. The music festivals have something to fit everyone's enjoyment. Do you love to golf? There are 7 amazing golf courses, 3 that are public. The White Mountains, where this home/cabin is - is the best kept secret of Arizona! Come and explore and enhance your living! Pinetop-Lakeside was also voted 'Best Cabin Region in the U.S"... Embrace the MAGIC!
